    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in good condition. The exterior has minor cosmetic blemishes consistent with normal use, but no significant damage. The interior shows some wear but remains clean and functional. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been reasonably maintained. A solid used car at a fair price.",
